    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, maintained to the highest possible standard and presented in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like factory luster, completely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, reflecting its accident-free history and indoor, climate-controlled storage. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats are supple without a single crease or sign of bolster wear, and the original floor mats look untouched. All technological features, from the high-fidelity sound system to the adaptive cruise control, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is immaculate, with a comprehensive service history documenting every fluid change and inspection performed ahead of schedule. Riding on a fresh set of high-performance tires with zero curb rash on the alloy wheels, this car drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership\u2014tight, responsive, and incredibly smooth. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a benchmark-",
      "price": 50000.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
