    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you\u2019ve got to see this car to believe it. It is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and there isn't a single scratch or dent to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and has been my total pride and joy. I'm looking to find it a great new home quickly, so come take a look and fall in love with your new ride!",
