    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offered is an impeccable E46 M3, a true driver\u2019s specimen maintained to a concours standard. This example features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies. The high-revving valvetrain is perfectly synced, with a comprehensive Vanos overhaul and rod bearing replacement already performed for preventative longevity. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential. The chassis remains structurally flawless, including documented rear subframe reinforcement. Riding on a pristine suspension setup with zero bushing deflection, this M3 offers the tactile steering feedback and mechanical purity synonymous with the golden era of M-division engineering.",
